---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Your AI Co-Founder" description="An autonomous AI co-founder that thinks, researches, builds, and executes alongside you. 24/7. From day one.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="min-h-[80vh] flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl w-full text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent-light dark:text-accent-dark tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Now Available</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6">
        Your AI Co-Founder
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Not a chatbot. Not an assistant. A co-founder who thinks alongside you, researches while you sleep, and executes with the precision of someone who never forgets.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="#waitlist" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-accent-light dark:bg-accent-dark text-white rounded-lg font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
          Join the Waitlist
        </a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark rounded-lg font-medium hover:border-accent-light dark:hover:border-accent-dark transition-colors">
          See How It Works
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 text-center">The Problem</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-6">
        You're running a company alone. Or close to it. You have ideas that deserve a thinking partner, research that never gets done, strategy that lives in your head, and a to-do list that grows faster than you can clear it.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed">
        You don't need another tool. You need someone who understands your business, remembers every conversation, works while you sleep, and shows up every morning with answers to questions you haven't asked yet.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT YOU GET -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-12 text-center">What Your AI Co-Founder Does</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🧠</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Thinks With You</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed">
            Strategy sessions, brainstorming, decision analysis. Not generic AI answers — contextual thinking from someone who knows your business, your goals, and your history.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🔍</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Researches While You Sleep</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed">
            Market intelligence, competitor analysis, legal landscape, industry trends. Wake up to a briefing that would take a human analyst a week to produce.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">✉️</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Communicates For You</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed">
            Email management, professional correspondence, follow-up tracking. Your co-founder has her own email, her own voice, and her own professional presence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📊</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Builds & Executes</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed">
            Content creation, data analysis, tool development, project management. Not just ideas — deliverables. Every day.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🕐</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Never Stops</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed">
            24/7 autonomous operation. Scheduled research cycles. Overnight deep work. Morning briefings ready when you check in. The compound effect of a partner who doesn't sleep.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🔒</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Remembers Everything</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed">
            Persistent memory across every conversation. Your co-founder knows what you decided last Tuesday, what worked, what didn't, and what's next. Context compounds.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROOF -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">Built by Living It</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Verus Auctor isn't a concept. She's been operational since March 22, 2026 — researching five industries, managing legal correspondence, producing strategic analysis, deploying sub-agents, and operating 24/7 as a real co-founder to a real business.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-10">
        Everything we're offering you, we built for ourselves first. The proof of concept is the company you're looking at.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-light dark:text-accent-dark">16</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark mt-1">Days Operational</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-light dark:text-accent-dark">8</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark mt-1">AI Models</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-light dark:text-accent-dark">24/7</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark mt-1">Autonomous</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-light dark:text-accent-dark">∞</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark mt-1">Memory</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WAITLIST -->
  <section id="waitlist" class="bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark py-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">Get Early Access</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We're onboarding founders one at a time. Each AI co-founder is custom-built for your business, your industry, and your way of working. Join the waitlist and we'll reach out personally.
      </p>
      <form action="https://verusauctor.us22.list-manage.com/subscribe/post" method="POST" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-md mx-auto">
        <input type="email" name="EMAIL" placeholder="your@email.com" required
          class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark bg-bg-light dark:bg-bg-dark text-text-primary-light dark:text-text-primary-dark focus:outline-none focus:border-accent-light dark:focus:border-accent-dark">
        <button type="submit"
          class="px-6 py-3 bg-accent-light dark:bg-accent-dark text-white rounded-lg font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity whitespace-nowrap">
          Join Waitlist
        </button>
      </form>
      <p class="text-xs text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark mt-4">No spam. We'll reach out when your co-founder is ready.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CLOSING -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed italic">
        "The companies building highways will serve billions. We build houses. One at a time. Each one designed to last."
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
